{"tid":688144,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"睇鹹片俾老豆發現，最後一齊睇","createTime":"2018-06-03T02:56:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T19:31:49.000Z","uid":42188,"like":74,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"c45a9624ece331b717e5dff70967c167760e80df","tid":688144,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T02:56:46.000Z","msg":"最近終於完sem啦<br />\n前排因為太忙<br />\n成個星期都冇打過J<br />\n於是襯啊媽出咗街就上網搵鹹片睇<br />\n搵搵下，搵到段「日本無碼14歲幼齒」<br />\n於是就睇啦<br />\n可能睇得太入神<br />\n連老豆返咗來都唔知<br />\n老豆望著我同埋個mon呆咗<br />\n我覺得好尷尬，因為俾老豆知道咗我竟然好呢味野...<br />\n但老豆就話：「衰仔，一齊睇啦，老豆後生個陣都成日睇，係結咗婚之後唔敢睇。」<br />\n我終於明白點解自己有呢種口味，原來係遺傳既<br />\n睇睇下，我發覺老豆下面都扯咗<br />\n於是我學鹹片裡面個男主角<br />\n主動幫老豆除褲含<br />\n老豆又學返另一個男主角幫我含<br />\n最後69，互相口爆<br />\n而事後，呢個就成為我同老豆既秘密，啊媽都唔知，嘻嘻"},{"pid":"e21707cc8c85aca7e03f05621b2efa43876e990c","tid":688144,"uid":67462,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T03:01:45.000Z","msg":"硬左"},{"pid":"b8e94e99cb75006c49d86ab3dac8031facc95432","tid":688144,"uid":163554,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T03:02:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80f94ee6f36bb52258a9927e1c2e882161967d91","tid":688144,"uid":42188,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"b8e94e99cb75006c49d86ab3dac8031facc95432","tid":688144,"uid":163554,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T03:02:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T03:03:10.000Z","msg":"好驚，唔報死全家"},{"pid":"db7ca41f81b80bd7194de0f2a03775bcf553ddb9","tid":688144,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T03:03:12.000Z","msg":"亂倫 刑事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb6113cf7b43618e73806a7f0eebf2ee41d18b88","tid":688144,"uid":132902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T03:05:05.000Z","msg":"我都鐘意14"},{"p